{"type": "article", "id": 47871, "title": "像拼图一样的凹凸桌，满足各种办公需求｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-03T22:57:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 46015, "name": "One of Those"}, {"id": 46016, "name": "Ooo My Design"}, {"id": 43058, "name": "众产品"}, {"id": 46017, "name": "Ember"}, {"id": 46018, "name": "CEDIT – Ceramiche d’Italia"}, {"id": 46019, "name": "Chen Bikovski"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 196, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171203212058nZXbvLY3zTWOE2xJ.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #5a5a5a; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5a5a5a} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #5a5a5a; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5a5a5a} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Storie collection by  Giorgia Zanellato &amp; Daniele Bortotto for CEDIT – Ceramiche d’Italia</h3><p>如今，很多人并不喜欢把家里装饰成全然新貌的样子，他们喜欢做旧一点，营造那种很有年代感的氛围。设计师 Giorgia Zanellato 和 Daniele Bortotto 最近为陶瓷品牌 CEDIT – Ceramiche d’Italia 设计了新墙板，意在让墙面呈现出破旧的怀旧感，融合了各种各样的效果，从传统壁画的褪色油漆、锈迹斑斑的砖石到潮湿的灰泥，就像是给墙纸制造“年轻错觉”一般。</p><p>用设计师的话说：“技术创新使我们能够在大尺寸的陶瓷材料上，创造出通常只有时间才能制造的磨损和分层效应。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212150tP9rxUE6Mu3hHyVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212151b9DeO78Uz4NJHKBq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212151KLsqjwgZn8Y3v9Vb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212151TESVfaApLyIGYrFR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212152LeDkCiT5lBuQrGKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/30/studio-zanellato-bortotto-storie-ceramic-slabs-wall-panels-illusion-age-cedit/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ember Ceramic Mug by Ember</h3><p>这款名为 Ember 的陶瓷咖啡杯，收获了 2017 年《时代》杂志的最佳发明之一。它使用陶瓷材料设计，内置蓝牙功能将马克杯和智能手机连接，就能在手机上设置你想要的饮用温度。</p><p>Ember 有五种温度可选，并且针对不同口味和饮品有专门定制的选项，如果觉得温度过高也可以手动进行选择适宜的温度，其次用户还可以自主选择杯子底部 LED 加热灯的颜色。如果在中途加入牛奶或者新的咖啡等，手机也会自动显示当前温度提醒你是否需要加热。售价 79.95 美元，<a href=\"https://ember.com/products/ceramic-mug\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712032123158RdqDgs94N5P7eFj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.132004\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212315zEHtkvgSGarwWyB9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212315pJQqc3KONUo5vlmA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614754\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212315y73eVrjXl0AEhkud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609400\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212316gU9Wh5FB8XpTxKQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610032\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>凹凸桌 by 众产品</h3><p>众产品团队最新推出的凹凸桌，能够满足各种不确定的办公空间使用需求。这组桌子像五块可以互相接合的拼图，鼓励用户发挥创造力，以多种方式使用每一张桌子。这些各自独立的桌子可拼为一条长会议桌，或是供小组讨论用的组合桌。</p><p>凹凸桌之间的整体拼接，是通过桌面与桌腿的咬合设计实现的，类似于中国传统的榫卯。每张桌子长方向衔接面的侧边沿均为斜边，且倾斜方向两两相反，拼接时就能互相承托；同时，桌子短方向的桌腿均向桌面以外突出一截，拼接时即和桌面形成咬合。组合后抬起任何一端都不会散架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212359fTZe67sNiJGFd5Xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212359aK2c3VThsbe7OJE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212359JqxNd6BO0HtEvWQl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600751\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212400fpjMFXDs9WwVBhib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212400rES1ILA9PcliN3WY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212400QKrHxlRCEoDqANgG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Popup Lighting by Chen Bikovski </h3><p>这组 Popup 灯具，灵感源自折纸书，希望能够为周边区域带来别样的氛围。光与空间的互动充满趣味与艺术，设计师用一系列装置将光源固定其中，不论动物还是植物的轮廓，亦或是金属或者木头的材质，通过这些灯具，你都可以制造自己的风格。售价 95 美元，<a href=\"https://popuplighting.com/collections/owl\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212428YVbnj1T07IhqiuGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212428oZb4rW8DjL9stkl5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212428OZSLAN2wpdo7CJ8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017120321242887jk4ewXM6nUSYFb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212428XsJSwUFe1PBkY29E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pinpres Shelf by Ooo My Design</h3><p>Pinpres 是一款可以包容你各种突发奇想的收纳架，出自西班牙设计工作室 Ooo My Design 之手。一颗颗长短一致的木钉密密麻麻地钉在一块木板上，通过伸缩木钉来调节存放空间的形状大小，无论任何形状物品都适合。</p><p>相较于我们传统使用的宽度和高度都已经固定的收纳架，Pinpres 的最大优势在于灵活。对于孩子而言，它也是一个可以激发创造力的玩具。PinPres 收纳架有多种不同颜色可选，底板为天然松木胶合板或白色油漆木板，木钉材料可以自由定制，也可以多种颜色混合或单色。售价 780 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/pinpres-ooo-my-design-06-15-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712032125310Y1aL3xIuipnE7O6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212531iBEj7a9hktuKpNyI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712032125316uI1MeVj3bmRSgLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212531rUb3do1cz4O8gtIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212531jsZV7axz5c6Wf9ph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.006036\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>One of Those Perfume</h3><p>意大利香水品牌 One of Those 给人的感觉就是简单、中性，圆柱形的透明瓶子看起来也是普普通通的包装。但其亮点在于外包装，估计没有哪个香水品牌会想到用聚苯乙烯来包装自己，就是我们常见的塑料泡沫。外壳上印着元素周期表上的各种元素，比如氢、氦、锂、碳、氧、硫等等，区分不同的香型。用户要使用香水，必须打破外包装才可以。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212600Irp9QymoTCvch3XU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.797778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212601rnifToDOu5R73pgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212602xA8a3nycvopkh14j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212602b0nfcoS2UKYgxytB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171203212602edhWNrTZwMg8z5Kq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712032126028AZ95BzGOr3Xu4H0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}